---
import ContentPageLayout from '../layouts/ContentPageLayout.astro';
---

<ContentPageLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Trees Puzzle"
  heading="Privacy Policy"
  description="Trees Puzzle privacy policy covering analytics, contact submissions, cookies, and user rights."
  canonicalPath="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <p>This Privacy Policy explains how Trees Puzzle may collect, use, and protect information when you browse the site, contact the editorial team, or interact with future downloadable resources.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">Information we may collect</h2>
  <p>We may collect basic technical data such as browser type, approximate IP-based location, referring page, and pages viewed. If you contact us directly, we may also receive your name, email address, and message content.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">How information is used</h2>
  <p>Information may be used to keep the site working, reply to messages, understand which pages are useful, improve content quality, and protect against spam or misuse.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">Cookies and analytics</h2>
  <p>The site may use essential cookies and may later add analytics or advertising tools. If third-party services are enabled, they may process data under their own privacy terms.</p>
  <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-white pt-4">Data requests</h2>
  <p>You can contact <a class="text-brand-400 hover:text-brand-300 transition-colors" href="mailto:hello@treespuzzle.com">hello@treespuzzle.com</a> with privacy questions or to request correction or deletion of personal data that you have submitted directly.</p>
</ContentPageLayout>
